Feedback























orix capital ltd
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Specialty Finance
Sub-Industry: Consumer Finance
Orix Capital Limited was founded in 1995. The Company's line of business includes providing loans to individuals as well as financing retail sales.




