Orix Capital Partners LLC: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback


























orix capital partners llc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Private Equity
Orix Capital Partners, LLC operates as a private equity firm. The Company makes direct controlling equity investments in middle-market companies throughout North America.




